    "faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_hiUJm9": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ingredients",
            "content": "<p><strong>Astaxanthin</strong> – Powerful antioxidant that helps protect the skin from oxidative stress and supports a healthy, radiant glow. <br/><br/><strong>L-Tyrosine</strong> – An amino acid involved in the body's natural melanin production, helping support a deeper, more even tan. <br/><br/><strong>Hyaluronic Acid</strong> – Helps maintain skin hydration and gives the skin a plumper, smoother appearance.<br/><br/><strong>Collagen</strong> – Supports skin firmness and elasticity while helping maintain youthful-looking skin.</p><p></p><p>☀️ Supports a natural golden glow<br/><br/>💧 Deeply hydrates the skin<br/><br/>✨ Promotes smoother, firmer skin<br/><br/>🛡️ Protects against oxidative stress caused by UV exposure<br/><br/>🌴 Helps achieve a more even-looking tan<br/><br/>💖 Supports healthy skin from within</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_iQzdhh": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "When will I start to see a tan?",
            "content": "<p>Most people see first results around week 4 Consistency is what matters most. And if you do get some sun, your natural tan and your gummy glow build on each other for a deeper, longer-lasting result. The molecule J Lycopene and Astaxanthin are awesome and reliable antioxidants. Maintain a glowing tan by eating yummy gummies? Yes!</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_QAUx9H": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How to use my Tanning gummies ?",
            "content": "<p>For best results, take 2 gummies with a meal and a glass of water.</p><p>Do not consume on an empty stomach. If you are sensitive to new supplements, start with just 1 gummy per day to assess your tolerance.</p><p>Enjoy your journey to a beautiful tan !</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_hzNLGm": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long will my delivery take?",
            "content": "<p>Due to exceptionally high demand, your Tanning Gummies will be delivered within approximately 8 days.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_mkzghj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you have a guarantee?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! If you are not satisfied with our Tanning Gummies, contact us and we will refund you fully.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
